graph LR
    %% AgentRx feedback loop from upstream issue #30

    Admin[👤 Admin User] --> UI[🖥️ Admin UI]
    UI --> Proposal[💡 Improvement Proposal<br/>Observed quality gap / desired behavior]
    Proposal --> AgentRx[🩺 AgentRx<br/>Analyze system + recommend changes]

    AgentRx --> Review{✅ Approve<br/>recommended changes?}
    Review -->|No| Refine[🔁 Revise proposal<br/>or keep for backlog]
    Refine --> Proposal

    Review -->|Yes| Orchestrator[🔐 Admin Change Orchestrator]

    subgraph Targets["Improvement Targets"]
        direction TB
        AgentCfg[🤖 Agent Configuration<br/>Top-level instruction updates]
        GenieCfg[🧞 Genie Configuration<br/>Add/remove tables and Genies<br/>Room-level instructions]
        MetadataCfg[🧱 Metadata / Smart ETL<br/>Columns, comments, abbreviations]
    end

    Orchestrator --> AgentCfg
    Orchestrator --> GenieCfg
    Orchestrator --> MetadataCfg

    AgentCfg --> AdminOps[⚙️ Admin-Level Operations]
    GenieCfg --> AdminOps
    MetadataCfg --> AdminOps

    AdminOps --> Refresh[🚀 Refresh deployed agent context<br/>and data access configuration]
    Refresh --> Runtime[💬 End User Runtime]
    Runtime --> Feedback[📈 Better accuracy, curation, and speed]
    Feedback -. informs .-> Admin

    classDef userClass fill:#E94B3C,stroke:#A33428,stroke-width:2px,color:#fff
    classDef agentClass fill:#4A90E2,stroke:#2E5C8A,stroke-width:2px,color:#fff
    classDef processClass fill:#F5A623,stroke:#C17D11,stroke-width:2px,color:#000
    classDef dataClass fill:#50C878,stroke:#2E7D4E,stroke-width:2px,color:#fff
    classDef decisionClass fill:#8E44AD,stroke:#6C3483,stroke-width:2px,color:#fff

    class Admin,Runtime userClass
    class UI,Proposal,Orchestrator,AdminOps,Refresh processClass
    class AgentRx,AgentCfg,GenieCfg,MetadataCfg agentClass
    class Feedback,Refine dataClass
    class Review decisionClass
